'''Kôn-yîm''', '''Kôn-sṳ-yîm''', '''Kôn-sṳ-yîm phù-sat''', tang tang hai [[Fut-kaau]] yit ko [[phù-sat]]. Hai [[chung kok]] fut-kau chui yiu mang ke phu-sat. Hi choi [[Fan-vun]] kiaau chu अवलोकितेश्वर/Avalokiteśvara. Kon-yim suk yue [[chung kok]] fut-kaau ke [[Si thaai phu-sat]] chi yit. 

Kôn-sṳ-yîm yiu saam-sap-ngie chung faa-sin. Hi kau-thu chung-sen. Fut-kaau fa Kon-yim fui kau chui chui-lan ke ngin. Fut-kaau yiu haau to kang-vun thung chau hai kong Kon-yim.

